[http://www.ruckuswireless.com/products/zoneflex-indoor/7341 7341/3 product page] This appears to be a AR71xx+AR922x device. 10/100/1000 PoE port + 2x 10/100 ports The '''Ruckus Wireless''' logo, "GD 11", and "220-11133[ ]Rev[ ] Ser." is silkscreened on the board. :"FAB 100-11133-001 REV 2" is on the opposite (component) side of the board. [http://www.speedguide.net/routers/ruckus-zoneflex-7343-single-band-wireless-access-2089 On SpeedGuide.net] :[http://pdf.ruckuscdn.com/datasheets/ds-zoneflex-7300-series.pdf 7300 series Datasheet] Default credentials are per the FCC label. :Per the FCC manual, the default SSID format is '''WirelessX''' (where '''X''' is a number).
